            <p><add hand="#barker">Acknowledging declaration of war against Tahuayas Indians.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            
<p><persName>Stephen F Austin</persName>, To the Most Excellent Deputation of Texas.</p>

<p>I am apprized of the declaration of War declared by the Most
Excellent diputation to the <persName>Tahuayas Nation</persName>, caused by their bad
conduct and hostile dispositions. I have given notice to the 
<persName>inhabitants </persName>to be very cautious, in order to avoid misfortunes on the part
of that <persName>tribe</persName>, or any other that may attempt an aggression</p>

<p>God and Liberty, <placeName>San Felipe de Austin</placeName>, <date when="1824-05-25">May 25th 1824,-4-3.</date></p>

<p><persName>Estevan F Austin</persName></p>

        </div1>
